name: Edward Snowden - Variant 03 - Decentral Eyes
description: Typography and image collage. Overlay of servers interweave Snowden's purchasing whistleblower servers anonymously using Bitcoin. Snowden dropped this knowledge bomb at BTC 2019 conference and I was lucky to be there. From 'Decentral Eyes' 3D portrait series. Created with 10+ images to create a decentralized portrait. This version available in physical rare 3D lenticular prints.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
